text: Nils Amund Røhne (20 April 1949 - 10 January 2022) was a Norwegian politician. He was a member of the Labour Party. He was born in Stange, Norway. From 1996 until 1997, he was State Secretary in the Ministry of Trade. He was also a member of the Storting from 1997 until 2009. Røhne died on 10 January 2022 in Oslo, Norway at the age of 72.Stange-ordfører Nils A. Røhne er død ==References== Category:1949 births Category:2022 deaths Category:Norwegian politicians
